                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220522-164-off863 t18220522-164-cd864"></join>, one coat, value 3 l.; one waistcoat, value 1 l.; one handkerchief, value 1 s., and one towel, value 6 d.
